snippet.title: Tannenberg: Wolf Truce Event Trailer!
snippet.description:
Wolves are on the hunt! Tannenberg is an authentic multiplayer WW1 shooter, and from November 26th until December 3rd you may find your battles invaded by packs of hungry canine hunters! Will you call a truce, or try to take advantage of the chaos? Join the wolf truce now!

Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/633460

About Tannenberg:
Tannenberg is a authentic World War I multiplayer first person shooter set on the Eastern Front. Battle through historic events in epic 64 player matches, with historical accurate squads, weaponry & uniforms! The game is developed and published by M2H & Blackmill Games and is part of the WW1 Game Series, with Verdun representing the Western Front. 

#WorldWarI #Tannenberg #WolfTruceEvent
